      "writtenOn": "2015-03-04T19:40:49Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Sure, we use emulator for CI, and we want to install some apk on it / run ativity tests, so we need an adb server. I can discard this change if you prefer.",
      "parentUuid": "321d9af7_d71cb367",
